{"word":"G3804 - πάθημα - páthēma - path'-ay-mah - Affection","slug":"G3804","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάθημα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>páthēma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>path'-ay-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Affection"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B1; - pathe&#x0304;ma</b> - <i>path'-ay-mah</i><p/>From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>; something <i>undergone</i>, that is, <i>hardship</i> or <i>pain</i>; subjectively an <i>emotion</i> or <i>influence:</i> - affection, affliction, motion, suffering."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>"}]}